Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.51,0:00:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦…就真的是梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.34,0:00:04.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.97,0:00:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是在猜谜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.21,0:00:11.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们有没有觉得一些梦境其实是真实的体验呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.72,0:00:12.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.07,0:00:16.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是在做梦的时候觉得这是在做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.18,0:00:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～我可能没有过…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.15,0:00:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也…不是没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.40,0:00:36.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱 万物归于沉寂的深夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.19,0:00:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我却发现 有时会听到火车的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.13,0:01:02.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说新威尼斯也有火车
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.22,0:01:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但从这里是听不到那么远的声音的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.08,0:01:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 这么晚根本就不会有火车在行驶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.05,0:01:14.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…是从天空传来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.39,0:01:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…是银河铁道…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:59.84,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(320,270)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那个 银河铁道之夜…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.29,0:03:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深夜传来火车的声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.55,0:03:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.18,0:03:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没听到过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 只有我听到了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.78,0:03:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 那今天也在那片树荫下休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华最近很喜欢那个地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:31.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里人又少 是个超级好地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.59,0:03:35.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…喂 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？夜空中的火车声？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.08,0:03:42.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.39,0:03:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听到过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.54,0:03:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起银河铁道 好像是某个著名小说里的东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.40,0:03:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有那个的图画书哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:58.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那是…开往死亡国度的列车…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.64,0:04:01.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里 你要小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.66,0:04:04.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你总是会吸引些奇奇怪怪的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.13,0:04:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半夜见到火车的话…千万不能坐上去…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.54,0:04:15.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华前辈你怕得太夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没有害怕啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.57,0:04:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我再讲个更恐怖的故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.49,0:04:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.23,0:04:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然…是我弄错了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.49,0:05:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.74,0:05:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个手印…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是只很大的猫咪呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.99,0:05:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长…这难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.96,0:05:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车票？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一日内有效车票
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.73,0:05:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tram大道 凌晨二时发车
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.98,0:05:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 银河铁道…？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.40,0:05:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日期是…明天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:05.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Caitsith对我发出的邀请吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那今天也在那片树荫下休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.57,0:06:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.04,0:06:24.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里 今天也停在那片树荫…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.18,0:06:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水无灯里小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.18,0:06:37.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦 灯里 为什么要叹气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.42,0:06:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么烦恼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.59,0:06:41.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不算是烦恼啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不算？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.64,0:06:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不知道怎么办好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前每次遇见他 总是会心跳不已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.96,0:06:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而现在也很想见到他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.23,0:06:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是怎么说呢…同时又觉得不要经常见面比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.07,0:07:06.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂喂 灯里…你…什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:08.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方是谁 是谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级意外的说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.12,0:07:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是马尾男？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可能是邮递员大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不是那样的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.84,0:07:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是怎么样的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…怎么说好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.49,0:07:24.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很慈祥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟他在一起会觉得很安心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.19,0:07:30.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有着非常光滑的毛皮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.87,0:07:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对了 尾巴也很漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.18,0:07:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尾巴…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.17,0:07:41.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里 虽然这有点不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.88,0:07:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道对方是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.41,0:07:44.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.20,0:07:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 为什么 不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.79,0:07:50.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要再大点…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.83,0:07:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猫咪的国王…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.19,0:07:55.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是Caitsith吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:07:57.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.50,0:08:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是不要再想他比较好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 一般都不会想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少我是不太想见到他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非你其实很胆小？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:13.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是谨慎而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.94,0:08:18.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但Caitsith就像万花筒一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次相遇 都能得到让人兴奋不已的体验
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和闪闪发光的奇迹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.79,0:08:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人害羞的台词 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.67,0:08:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 继续练习吧 练习！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.95,0:08:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.50,0:08:43.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tram大道 就在这前面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.74,0:08:55.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里对吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:09:02.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长 这里看上去走不了火车呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.06,0:09:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:09:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:13.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银河铁道的车票啊 不是很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.77,0:10:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不是应该不去比较好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.49,0:10:29.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不觉得害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.07,0:10:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该说是深不可测吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.78,0:10:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是我遇到的奇妙之事 还是Caitsith
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.02,0:10:43.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像包围着AQUA的大海一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.98,0:10:47.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大海…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:53.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 宽广而又深沉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 在他的怀抱中又非常地平静
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.73,0:11:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里想要邂逅更多AQUA的美好和奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.19,0:11:08.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直想要更加了解AQUA 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.95,0:11:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.54,0:11:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是说不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.93,0:11:20.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AQUA说不定也很想更加了解灯里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得AQUA好像在尝试着对灯里敞开心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AQUA的…心…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.28,0:11:55.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里想要邂逅更多AQUA的美好和奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:12:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直想要更加了解AQUA 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…现在也是这样想的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:14.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长 准备就绪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.31,0:12:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行驶在AQUA的夜空中的银河铁道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.66,0:12:28.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的能见到的话 就太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:34.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之我们先去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:12:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里…是Tram大道…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:08.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真安静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.99,0:15:09.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没带车票吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不介意的话请用我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.19,0:15:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…那个…这张票还是给这只小猫咪用吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.76,0:16:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.66,0:16:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是Caitsith先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.93,0:16:27.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在墓地之岛救了我的 就是您吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.22,0:16:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时真是谢谢您了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.41,0:16:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有…谢谢您今天的邀请…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.37,0:17:21.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是…从哪里来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:25.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候出现在AQUA的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 愿意出现在我面前呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:44.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 总是默默地守护着我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您…到底是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.00,0:18:01.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又大…又温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非您是…您是AQUA的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.87,0:18:33.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.78,0:18:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.23,0:20:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那果然是银河铁道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.78,0:20:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:06.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天我们能坐上去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦…？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.61,0:21:13.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那原来不是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.15,0:21:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然没能坐上银河铁道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.69,0:21:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但Caitsith还是给我盖了章
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.10,0:21:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然想更多地了解 却又感到有些许害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.63,0:21:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然想更加地接近 却又不知彼此的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.05,0:21:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也许 双方都踏出了自己的第一步呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.37,0:21:49.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个图章也许是想对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.06,0:21:53.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要忘记我们的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.95,0:21:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.26,0:21:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.65,0:22:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一想到Caitsith也许就是AQUA之心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.88,0:22:09.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像…实在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.22,0:22:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱 这是前所未有的兴奋感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.29,0:22:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且 使我对以后的那许多的邂逅憧憬不已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.76,0:22:30.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猫咪的图章 真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.11,0:22:34.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次我也想让他在额头上「嘭」地盖一个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.50,0:22:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里姐姐 我也在兴奋地憧憬着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.85,0:22:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想在AQUA邂逅更多的美好奇迹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.99,0:22:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟灯里姐姐一起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.02,0:24:11.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 不可思议的世界…\N那位 AQUA的守护者啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.23,0:01:36.13,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}窓からそっと 朝陽がのびて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.52,0:01:49.11,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}まどろむまつ毛に こぼれてくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.45,0:02:04.15,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}そよふく風 部屋へと招いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.19,0:02:16.96,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}木漏れ日に 君の寝顔 優しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.34,0:02:16.96,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an7}Euforia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.06,0:02:23.28,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}いつものありふれた朝だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.96,0:02:30.89,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}鮮やかに色づいてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.16,0:02:38.37,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}それは君と巡り合えた奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.95,0:02:41.91,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}ひとりじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.47,0:02:48.68,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}君と一緒にいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.23,0:01:36.13,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}晨曦悄然漫入窗际
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.52,0:01:49.11,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}洒落在 舒睡的睫毛间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.45,0:02:04.15,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}让轻拂的风吹入小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.19,0:02:16.96,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}枝叶间滑落的阳光 映衬你的睡颜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.34,0:02:16.96,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an3}Euforia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.06,0:02:23.28,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}虽是个平凡无奇的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.96,0:02:30.89,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}也染上了艳丽的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.16,0:02:38.37,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}那正是与你邂逅的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.95,0:02:41.91,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我并非孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.47,0:02:48.68,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}因为 有你相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【EDJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.76,0:23:00.18,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}去りゆく夏の日 思いを寄せて集うバルコニー
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.98,0:23:17.67,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}水面にきらめく風のゴンドラ いま滑り出す
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.07,0:23:31.80,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}流れる時の河でめぐり逢えた人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.60,0:23:42.78,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}いま夜空を焦がして輝く夏の夜の夢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.76,0:23:53.04,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}忘れないでSmile Again いつまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【EDCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.76,0:23:00.18,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}即将逝去的夏日 怀抱着思念来到露台上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.98,0:23:17.67,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}在水面上闪耀着 那风之凤尾舟 正要启航
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.07,0:23:31.80,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}不断流逝的时间长河中 人们彼此邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.60,0:23:42.78,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}划过长夜之空的是那炫目的夏夜之梦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.76,0:23:53.04,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}请不要忘记Smile Again 无论何时
